{"tid":595543,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"李嘉誠對走資說法只能置之一笑　稱做生意買賣是正常","createTime":"2018-03-16T17:46:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-17T01:47:45.000Z","uid":70274,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"14500d67adb0165592395b858bd3efd84cf82865","tid":595543,"uid":70274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T17:46:38.000Z","msg":"香港電台-港聞<br />\n<br />\n李嘉誠退任長和及長實集團主席及執董。<br />\n李嘉誠在長和系業績記者會表示，一般連經濟知識都沒有的人才會講「走資」，自己在一邊賣走資產，在另一邊再購買。<br />\n<br />\n他說，錢走回香港，以及錢投資在內地，全部錢都是屬於公司，自己對走資的說法只能置之一笑，認為做生意買賣是正常。<br />\n李嘉誠說，無論自己買賣甚麼都好，錢全都走入公司，自己得不到錢，錢及資產是屬於公司，如果要走資是需要現金，並對公司無興趣，只可以賣股票，才會有真金白銀。<br />\n他表示，公司在中國南海有400億出產天然氣的項目，規模有可能會再加大，又提到公司是北京東方廣場的大股東。"},{"pid":"f3bc9bb45069d554a9b9daa412b53f48298c15d5","tid":595543,"uid":102198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T00:49:14.000Z","msg":"cc台手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9aa7791fb5524441f8323a757b126c2a69effa77","tid":595543,"uid":76855,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T00:51:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.mingpaocanada.com/TOR/ftp/News/20170830/HK/_30MB004_.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mingpaocanada.com%2FTOR%2Fftp%2FNews%2F20170830%2FHK%2F_30MB004_.jpg&h=80975742&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"10b3ddeb1fefba50b53c5bb08a4c4a7979bd1f03","tid":595543,"uid":75692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9aa7791fb5524441f8323a757b126c2a69effa77","tid":595543,"uid":76855,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T00:51:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.mingpaocanada.com/TOR/ftp/News/20170830/HK/_30MB004_.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mingpaocanada.com%2FTOR%2Fftp%2FNews%2F20170830%2FHK%2F_30MB004_.jpg&h=80975742&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T00:52:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7df4f61a93915fe7c4a1dd2db823e904ea4a7e73","tid":595543,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T00:54:01.000Z","msg":"賣私人資產就話姐<br />\n<br />\n賣公司資產又無似大劉咁派特別股息<br />\n錢又回塘香港上市公司 走乜資"},{"pid":"032c425bc79164081cfb0055033599314b07cb6c","tid":595543,"uid":35092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7df4f61a93915fe7c4a1dd2db823e904ea4a7e73","tid":595543,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T00:54:01.000Z","msg":"賣私人資產就話姐<br />\n<br />\n賣公司資產又無似大劉咁派特別股息<br />\n錢又回塘香港上市公司 走乜資"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T01:10:56.000Z","msg":"賣私人資產都唔關 9 佢事啦 ... 我自己野，仲意賣就賣啦，關佢撚事。"},{"pid":"97bfb94fdd7446bf911bafe5e7ee4280d89f33b7","tid":595543,"uid":85284,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T01:39:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: blue;\">一般連經濟知識都沒有的人才會講「走資」</span><br />\n<br />\n咁都叫做唔呃人？"},{"pid":"db0351dacff1083e8eaba12cbd91d98eb3022350","tid":595543,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T01:47:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />超人又9up"}]}